			<li>Fika Places will share your information with 3rd parties only if you have given consent for us to do so. These 3rd parties may use your information to contact you with regards to the specific event or other relevant events you may be interested in, based on your purchase history.</li><br>
			<li>Fika Places will not share you information, we will always respect your privacy and any personal communication between you and ourselves. We will always comply with data protection legislation set out by the Republic of Kenya.</li><br>
